leizi-shell (1.3.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New release: v1.3.0 - User Experience & Documentation
  * Add syntax highlighting system (Fish Shell style)
  * Add performance optimizations (2ms startup, 2ms prompt)
  * Add memory safety tools (AddressSanitizer, UBSan, TSan)
  * Add configuration system with INI-style files
  * Add smart completion with provider pattern
  * Add comprehensive documentation (500+ lines)
  * Add Git status caching optimization

